{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/bi_logo_text_horizontal_616x49.png?t=1717166010\" /><br>Bass Invaders is a rhythmic fusion of classic shoot 'em up and live audio analysis.<br><br>Battle to the other side of the galaxy on a mission to save the Earth in a campaign mode with a genre-spanning soundtrack, or load <i>literally any song</i> and experience your favourite music in a new way.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/shoot_hold_rotate_L06.gif?t=1717166010\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/UNLIMITED_MUSIC_LIBRARY.png?t=1717166010\" /><br>Play using any song you like, loading from your own files or using online video. Any track, any time. No limits.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/BEAT_THE_BEST.png?t=1717166010\" /><br>High scores and ranked leaderboards for every song. Fill your ship energy levels to unleash power mode. Nail that perfect run and show your skill.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/FIND_YOUR_FLOW.png?t=1717166010\" /><br>Five difficulty levels so you can just enjoy the music or really challenge your skills.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/SAVE_THE_WORLD.png?t=1717166010\" /><br>Launch into a galaxy spanning campaign mode as Ace and PZO-116 battle to save the world from alien invaders. Enjoy every level with its own custom song from a genre-spanning soundtrack.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/FUN_WITH_FRIENDS.png?t=1717166010\" /><br>Two-player local co-op in e